You are here: SALESFORCE HELP > SERVICE CLOUD > Einstein Bots Chat

Lighten the load on your support agents with automated chat bots that can address straightforward issues or questions from your customers.

The legacy chat product is scheduled for retirement on February 14, 2026. You receive 25 Einstein Bots conversations per month for each active Digital Engagement user. You can buy a subscription for an additional 100 Einstein Bots conversations per month for use in one org.

Salesforce has the right to terminate your access to Einstein Bots if there is any unauthorized use.

Chat with Customers with Einstein Bots
title: Automated Chat Bots for Customer Support
